$cat test

This is an ASCII file

-If I want to convert all the characters in test file to Uppercase

$dd if=test of=out conv=ucase

if-input file
of-output file

There are hell a lot of things that can be done with dd, with dd we canformat diskdrive and floppy drives
conv iso file of os and install

$dd if=test of=out conv=ebcdic

conv ASCII test to European format
